

Telegram : 
For a new user to onboard the telegram bot we need to do the following. 

to set webhook for your bot you need to run the following request : 

https://api.telegram.org/bot<YOUR_BOT_TOKEN>/setWebhook?url=<BAECKEND_END_POINT>/api/webhooks/telegram/onboard/



Whast app : 
to setup a web hook for whats app please go to 
Sand box and setup the when a message comes in  to the URL of our backend, 

![alt text](image.png)


https://<Backedn_URL>/api/webhooks/twilio/whatsapp/

consider we have the following backend : 
Backedn_URL : suzann-inexpugnable-laylah.ngrok-free.dev

in twillo The URL will be : 

https://suzann-inexpugnable-laylah.ngrok-free.dev/api/webhooks/twilio/whatsapp/



for call back URL please use the following URL : 

https://<Backedn_URL>/api/callbacks/twilio/whatsapp/status/

which will be : 

https://suzann-inexpugnable-laylah.ngrok-free.dev/api/callbacks/twilio/whatsapp/status/







